  h1.gist_green
    | 更新も簡単！適正な人員配置を常に実現！
  = image_tag 'speed_update.jpg', class: 'top_image'
.vertically_aligned_and_centered
  h1.gist_orange
    | もう残業なんてさせません！！
  = image_tag 'at_the_end.jpg', class: 'top_image_last'
